From: Anurag <anurag.gopinath@broadcom.com>
Date: Tue, 27 Nov 2012 12:46:23 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 430/565] AHCI : Disable AHCI for XLP3XX Lite.

AHCI : Disable AHCI for XLP3XX Lite.

Based on Broadcom SDK 2.3.

Signed-off-by: Anurag <anurag.gopinath@broadcom.com>
Signed-off-by: Yanjiang Jin <yanjiang.jin@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/ata/ahci.c | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/ata/ahci.c b/drivers/ata/ahci.c
index 206e1a8..4b4b652 100644
--- a/drivers/ata/ahci.c
+++ b/drivers/ata/ahci.c
@@ -46,6 +46,7 @@
 #include <scsi/scsi_host.h>
 #include <scsi/scsi_cmnd.h>
 #include <linux/libata.h>
+#include <asm/netlogic/hal/nlm_hal_xlp_dev.h>
 #include "ahci.h"
 
 #define DRV_NAME	"ahci"
@@ -1198,6 +1199,10 @@ static int ahci_init_one(struct pci_dev *pdev, const struct pci_device_id *ent)
 		return -ENODEV;
 
 	if (pdev->vendor == PCI_VENDOR_ID_NETLOGIC && pdev->device == 0x101A) {
+                if (is_nlm_xlp3xx_lite()) {
+                    dev_printk(KERN_INFO, &pdev->dev, "No SATA interface on XLP3XX lite board\n");
+                    return -1;
+                }
 		ahci_pci_bar = 0;
                 nlm_xlp_nativesata = 1;
         }
